.DT
modify_item
Disk World creator help
modify_item

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
modify_item -  This method will modify certain bits of the specified item.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int modify_item(string word,
mixed new_desc)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^word%^RESET%^ - the name of the item to change
%^BOLD%^new_desc%^RESET%^ - the bits of the item to change
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/basic_room.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method will modify certain bits of the specified item.  This will
change only the bits of the pattern that are specified.  If you wish to
remove elements a better method would be to remove the item and
then readd it.  The format of the new_desc array is the same as in the
add_item code.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
remove_item(), add_item()

.EP

